Params: {3: 'After turning off the program in the sandbox system, Freeman walks out of the holographic simulation pod.'}
{2: 'Freeman', 3: 'This test is different than all the previous ones.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Recalling the events in the simulation, Freeman documents his discoveries and speculations on his terminal.'}
{2: 'Freeman', 3: 'Emphasize the cooperation among commandants... The deployment of multiple squads... Multidomain operations...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'As he types out his discoveries one by one on his terminal, his thoughts gradually become clear.'}

{2: 'Freeman', 3: "The surface circumstances don't align with the propaganda... The enemy is no longer in disarray... Is there a chance to unban some smart military equipment, or is it just an imaginary enemy within the Clean Zone?", 4: '1'}
{3: 'After tying out his final speculation, Freeman puts his terminal away.'}
{3: 'His gaze falls upon the application in the draft box before he walks out of the room.'}
{2: 'Freeman', 3: 'Nina, what do you want for dinner today?', 4: '1'}
